          "id": "tldr:2023-05-17:o005",
          "order": 1,
          "title": "GUIDANCE",
          "summary": "Guidance enables developers to control modern language models more effectively and efficiently than traditional prompting or chaining. It allows users to merge generation, prompting, and logical control into a single continuous flow, matching how the language model actually processes the text. Guidance features a simple, intuitive syntax, playground-like streaming, smart seed-based generation caching, support for role-based chat models, and easy integration with HuggingFace models.",
          "url": "https://github.com/microsoft/guidance?utm_source=tldrnewsletter",
          "reading_time_minutes": null,
          "source_domain": "github.com",
          "content_type": "github_repo",
          "is_sponsor": false
        },
        {
          "id": "tldr:2023-05-17:o006",
          "order": 2,
          "title": "TAILWIND VARIANTS",
          "summary": "Tailwind Variants combines the power of Tailwind with a first-class variant API. It features slots, responsive variants, component composition, and more. Tailwind Variants offers TypeScript auto-completion and type-safety. It is framework agnostic and it efficiently merges conflicting styles.",
